column5: Hey guys, does anyone know if lake St. John has ice? Will be up in that area over the weekend, would like to try that lake for eyes.
I would imagine, as couch now has 7".
Friday's warm weather and rain may change that...unless its significantly colder up that way. We expect 10 degrees and rain tomorrow in Guelph
Not sure how it will be after tomorrow's warm spell and rain! Be careful if you do go out! We're thinking of going out Sun. but quite a bit further north!
